<plot>In a small agricultural village in northern Israel, on the day of the middle-sister's wedding, Maya (Avital Abrajill), the youngest of the 3 sisters, arrives to the celebration with Alon (Dan Turgeman), a sharp Israeli businessman living in London. Alon's enchantment with the close-knit family, the simplicity of village life and serene landscape, opens his heart to an almost unattainable closeness with Tamar (Ayelet Zorer), the oldest sister, and re-acquaintance with his alienated father.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?360084</url></doc>
